#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.128"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.128:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.128:0.2"
msgid "13. Bhayavagga "
msgstr "13. Fears "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.128:0.3"
msgid "128. Dutiyatathāgataacchariyasutta "
msgstr "128. Incredible Things About the Realized One (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.128:1.1"
msgid "“Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā cattāro acchariyā abbhutā dhammā pātubhavanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, with the appearance of a Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha, four incredible and amazing things appear. "

msgctxt "an4.128:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: Ālayārāmā → ālayarāmā (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.128:1.3"
msgid "Ālayārāmā, bhikkhave, pajā ālayaratā ālayasammuditā; "
msgstr "People like attachment, they love it and enjoy it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:1.4"
msgid "sā tathāgatena anālaye dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti. "
msgstr "Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of non-adherence, they want to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:1.5"
msgid "Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ paṭhamo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati. "
msgstr "This is the first incredible and amazing thing that appears with the appearance of a Realized One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.132, sc2
msgctxt "an4.128:2.1"
msgid "Mānārāmā, bhikkhave, pajā mānaratā mānasammuditā. "
msgstr "People like conceit, they love it and enjoy it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:2.2"
msgid "Sā tathāgatena mānavinaye dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti. "
msgstr "Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of removing conceit, they want to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:2.3"
msgid "Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ dutiyo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati. "
msgstr "This is the second incredible and amazing thing that appears with the appearance of a Realized One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.128:3.1"
msgid "Anupasamārāmā, bhikkhave, pajā anupasamaratā anupasamasammuditā. "
msgstr "People like excitement, they love it and enjoy it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:3.2"
msgid "Sā tathāgatena opasamike dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti. "
msgstr "Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of peace, they want to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:3.3"
msgid "Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ tatiyo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati. "
msgstr "This is the third incredible and amazing thing that appears with the appearance of a Realized One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.128:4.1"
msgid "Avijjāgatā, bhikkhave, pajā aṇḍabhūtā pariyonaddhā. "
msgstr "This population is lost in ignorance, trapped in their shells. "

msgctxt "an4.128:4.2"
msgid "Sā tathāgatena avijjāvinaye dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti. "
msgstr "Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of removing ignorance, they want to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand it. "

msgctxt "an4.128:4.3"
msgid "Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ catuttho acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati. "
msgstr "This is the fourth incredible and amazing thing that appears with the appearance of a Realized One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.128:4.4"
msgid "Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ime cattāro acchariyā abbhutā dhammā pātubhavantī”ti. "
msgstr "With the appearance of a Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha, four incredible and amazing things appear.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.128:4.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

